data.description: **Both bathrooms are currently being remodeled** Bungalow style home being sold 'As Is' located on a large corner lot in Terrell Heights near Alamo Heights! This charming and cozy single-story home has hardwood flooring throughout and large windows with accent shutters. The kitchen has a tiled breakfast bar with an additional connecting satillo tiled floored room that can be used as an office or sun room with access doors to the attached garage behind the home as well as the driveway. Not only is Terrell Heights situated minutes north of downtown San Antonio, you will also have the opportunity to take advantage of everything Alamo Heights has to offer such as excellent schools , shopping and golfing in The Quarry and a strong sense of community!
